    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Caffeine will be studied against placebo in patients with positional headache after a lumbar
      puncture (aka &quot;spinal headache&quot;).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pain will be assessed at set intervals using a Visual Analog Scale. Blood patch therapy will
      be offered to all those still in pain at the end of one hour after drug administration.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
